@endnode

@node Bugs
The  "Load  Ansi"-option  is not bullet-proof - I will fix it RSN.  Loading
Ansi  files  is  a  little  "insecure",  as  only  ansi color sequences are
recognized.   If  an  odd ansi sequence is encountered, it is probable that
the rest of that line is lost in the Great Void.

If  you  find  any  bugs,  email me.  The program does some checking to not
screw  your  memory, but errors are not trapped in any way.  The proggy was
compiled  with  the "error message" setting set to "Yes", so you should get
an  error  message if the program crashes without crashing the whole system
with it.


                               K.Veijalainen
                        Email:  veijalai@cc.lut.fi
                      Address: 04940 Levanto, Finland
@endnode

