programs  (and ten zillion times better freeware progs :-) You may copy and
spread the program freely, but if you use it regularly, blah blah (standard
shareware  disclaimer).   If  you use the program regularly AND do not pay,
I'll  send  the  boys  (Vito  &  Bruno).  Send me the equal of 2 US$ in any
currency.   Not  much, huh?  Send it as cash - it's easiest that way, and I
can  always  use  strange  currencies  to  register shareware programs from
Swaziland  myself.   And  if someone steals the envelope, he/she/it will be
much  happier  if there is some cash inside.  All that the registered users
will  (hopefully) receive is a clean conscience - and maybe Santa will give
them  more  presents  next  X-Mas  (I don't have time to send them anything
except maybe email containing a nice ascii pic :-D ).  My address is in the
end of this doc file.

Oh,  and  one more thing:  If someone's hard drive gets formatted, computer
explodes  or  a  serious case of Bill Gatesness strikes (or anything at all
